know how in your mailboxes,

00:07:18.820 --> 00:07:21.560
you've got your mailbox, you've
got you inbox and your outbox,

00:07:21.560 --> 00:07:23.700
so you can see what you sent.

00:07:23.700 --> 00:07:25.150
Well, back then, people

00:07:25.150 --> 00:07:27.070
like George Washington
kept letter books.

00:07:27.070 --> 00:07:30.020
And, what they were,
were literally big books

00:07:30.020 --> 00:07:33.710
where they kept copies of
the letters that they wrote.

00:07:33.710 --> 00:07:36.890
And so, if you go into the
