00:07:36.890 --> 00:07:40.420
from the spring of 1787,
there is a copy of the letter

00:07:40.420 --> 00:07:42.110
that he sent to Henry Knox.

00:07:42.110 --> 00:07:44.700
And then, in another
collection is the response

00:07:44.700 --> 00:07:46.550
that he received
