00:07:46.550 --> 00:07:50.170
But, in the letter, he says my
dear sir, and then he goes on,

00:07:50.170 --> 00:07:51.500
he goes on, he goes
on, and then he gets

00:07:51.500 --> 00:07:52.920
into the meat of the letter.

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:54.770
And, what he asks is this.

00:07:54.770 --> 00:07:59.890
He says, this again,
it's March 1787.

00:07:59.890 --> 00:08:03.270
The Constitutional Convention
doesn't even begin until May.

00:08:03.270 --> 00:08:05.640
And, he's saying to George,
he's saying to Henry Knox,

00:08:05.640 --> 00:08:08.120
