been asked to go

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:10.290
to this convention
in Philadelphia.

00:08:10.290 --> 00:08:12.370
And, I'm deciding whether
or not I'm going to go.

00:08:12.370 --> 00:08:15.190
And, I'd really like
your advice.

00:08:15.190 --> 00:08:16.910
That's the essence
of this letter.

00:08:16.910 --> 00:08:24.560
He's saying a thought, however,
has lately run through my mind

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:26.650
which is attended
with embarrassment.

00:08:26.650 --> 00:08:28.660
It is whether my nonattendance

00:08:28.660 --> 00:08:31.690
at this convention will not
be considered as a dereliction

00:08:31.690 --> 00:08:36.650
to republicanism nay more
whether other motives may not,

00:08:36.650 --> 00:08:40.780
however injuriously, be ascribed
to me for not exerting myself

00:08:40.780 --> 00:08:42.750
on this occasion
in support of it.

00:08:42.750 --> 00:08:44.290
And he goes back and forth.

00:08:44.290 --> 00:08:45.590
And so, it's wonderful letter.

00:08:45.590 --> 00:08:46.890
And, you know, George
Washington,

00:08:46.890 --> 00:08:49.560
it's not language
that we hear today.

00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:53.100
But, the wishy washiness of
it is really incredible to me

00:08:53.100 --> 00:08:55.430
because take for granted
that George Washington went

00:08:55.430 --> 00:08:57.850
to the convention, that
he becomes the President

00:08:57.850 --> 00:08:59.150
of the Convention

00:08:59.150 --> 00:09:03.500
