and do research as well.

00:47:31.210 --> 00:47:33.990
And, of course, we want you to
all become our interns one day

00:47:33.990 --> 00:47:36.640
and then our colleagues.

00:47:36.640 --> 00:47:39.320
First of all thank you again
to the Levinsons thanks to all

00:47:39.320 --> 00:47:43.060
of you, hope you have a terrific
Constitution Day and a big shout

00:47:43.060 --> 00:47:44.960
out at your teachers
to getting you here.

00:47:44.960 --> 00:47:46.280
Thank you all very, very much.

